Plot of the VCF against the different bands

There seems to be a relation between band3/band7 and the VCF. On The orher hand, band4 doesn’t seem to show any relation.

Significant influence of the bands on VCF

The column of the PR(>|t| ) shows the significances between the bands and the VCF tree cover. All bands seem to be significant, so all of them are taken into account for the prediction model.

Root mean square error between predicted and actual tree cover

Formulae to calculate the RMSE: sqrt(mean((vcfGewata@data@values - pred_lm@data@values)^2, na.rm=TRUE))
